titles.title: A resolution honoring Miami University for its 200 years of commitment to public higher education.

vote.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment and with a preamble by Unanimous Consent.

reference.label: text as passed Senate; text of measure as introduced: CR S2163
reference.ref: text as passed Senate; text of measure as introduced: CR S2163

bill.summary: 2/11/2009--Passed Senate without amendment. (This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.) Congratulates Miami University, in Ohio, on its 200th anniversary. Expresses the Senate's best wishes for its continued success.
